sequenceDiagram
    participant Client1 as Client 1<br/>Alice
    participant Client2 as Client 2<br/>Bob  
    participant WS as WebSocket Server<br/>STOMP Broker
    participant StatusSvc as Status Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    Note over Client1,WS: Initial Connection
    
    Client1->>WS: CONNECT<br/>Authorization: Bearer JWT
    WS->>WS: Validate JWT
    WS->>Client1: CONNECTED
    
    Client2->>WS: CONNECT<br/>Authorization: Bearer JWT
    WS->>WS: Validate JWT
    WS->>Client2: CONNECTED
    
    Note over Client1,WS: Subscriptions
    
    Client1->>WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/status
    WS->>Client1: RECEIPT
    
    Client2->>WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/status
    WS->>Client2: RECEIPT
    
    Note over Client1,WS: Status Update Event
    
    Client1->>StatusSvc: Update status via REST
    StatusSvc->>DB: Save new status
    StatusSvc->>WS: SEND /topic/status<br/>{userId: Alice, status: IN_OFFICE}
    
    Note over WS: Broadcast to all<br/>subscribed clients
    
    WS->>Client1: MESSAGE {update}
    WS->>Client2: MESSAGE {update}
    
    Client1->>Client1: Update own row
    Client2->>Client2: Update Alice's row
    
    Note over Client1,WS: Graceful Disconnect
    
    Client1->>WS: DISCONNECT
    WS->>Client1: RECEIPT
    WS->>WS: Clean up subscription
    
    Note over Client2: Client2 still<br/>subscribed
